<lyrics>[V1]
.     Dm    Am
 Kóktegi Ákemiz,
.   Gm    Dm                Gm
 Kıeli esimiń qasterlene bersin!
.Dm      A            Dm
 Patshalyǵyń jerge kelsin!
.Dm       Gm     Am    Dm
 Erkiń Kókte oryndalǵandaı,
.Am        Gm     Dm
 Jerde de, oryndalsyn!
.Dm                   Am Gm Dm
 Kúndelikti nanymyzdy, bere gór!
.Dm
 Kinálini keshirgendeı,
.Gm                Dm
 Kúnámizdi keshire gór!
.Dm         Am   Dm
 Jamandyqqa túsirmeı,
.Dm          Am Gm  Dm
 Azǵyndyqtan saqtaı gór!</lyrics>
<title>Kóktegi Ákemiz Қак16</title>
